<p><strong>Kosciessa, J. Q.</strong>, Lindenberger, U. &amp; Garrett, D. D. (2020). Thalamocortical excitability adjustments guide human perception under uncertainty. Manuscript submitted for publication.</p>

<p><img class="img-responsive" src="http://localhost:4000/images/MAAT.gif" style="width: 400px" /></p>

<p>Multi-attribute-task used in Kosciessa, J. Q., Lindenberger, U., &amp; Garrett, D. D. (2020). Thalamocortical excitability adjustments guide human perception under uncertainty.</p>

<p>The code is provided <a href="https://git.mpib-berlin.mpg.de/LNDG/multi-attribute-task">here</a>.</p>
